                    "Michael Adeniyi Agbolade Ishola Adenuga is a Nigerian billionaire business man, born in Ibadan, Oyo state. His father, Mike Adenuga Snr, was a school teacher while his mother, Juliana Oyindamola Adenuga was a businesswoman of royal Ijebu decent.\n\n" +
